WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:58.820
Once there was the Sun
Bright and warm and wonderful

00:00:58.820 --> 00:01:05.120
Shining like the love within my heart

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:07.970
Now there’s no more sun
Winter

00:01:07.970 --> 00:01:14.280
Has killed everything
And although it’s dark December

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:16.280
Forever
I’ll remember sun

